0271+  7F10             ;
0272+  7F10             ; bitmap table -- bit patterns to put on the screen to
0273+  7F10             ;       display hex characters 0-F in a 5-high by 8-wide
0274+  7F10             ;       format. Each pattern uses 5 consecutive bytes.
0275+  7F10             ;       1's are bright, 0's are dark pixels. The patterns
0276+  7F10             ;       overlap to save memory.
0277+  7F10             bitmap:
